    <item>
      <title>助手中断采访后，麦莉的加密抗辩反对反对。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/milei-s-crypto-defense-backfires-after-aide-interrupts-interview</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统哈维尔·麦利（Javier Milei）偶然发现了他在加密丑闻中的角色，在该丑闻中，他吹捧了后来坠毁的成员，后来在投资者从美国假期返回后，后果扩散到了阿根廷资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/milei-s-crypto-defense-backfires-after-aide-interrupts-interview</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 14:31:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）法官对司法部的审理进行了听证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/adams-judge-sets-hearing-on-doj-move-to-drop-corruption-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）负责腐败案件的联邦法官安排了关于司法部撤销指控的要求的听证会，并表示他想解释政府这样做的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/adams-judge-sets-hearing-on-doj-move-to-drop-corruption-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 14:05:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和俄罗斯见面，与Zelenskiy交谈乌克兰和平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/us-and-russia-agree-to-more-talks-on-ukraine-set-no-summit-date</link>
      <description><![CDATA[来自美国和俄罗斯的高级官员开会对乌克兰的战争进行了第一轮谈判，但由于唐纳德·特朗普总统寻求迅速解决冲突，尽管有疏远欧洲盟友，但该国的领导人将这一领导人排除在会议之外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/us-and-russia-agree-to-more-talks-on-ukraine-set-no-summit-date</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 13:35:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Zelenskiy被排除在我们时，与俄罗斯讨论了乌克兰的命运</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/zelenskiy-out-in-cold-as-us-discusses-ukraine-s-fate-with-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统沃迪米尔·泽伦斯基（Volodymyr Zelenskiy）意外地取消了他对沙特阿拉伯的访问，因为他在美国和俄罗斯在他的国家的未来就被拒之门外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/zelenskiy-out-in-cold-as-us-discusses-ukraine-s-fate-with-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 13:31:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列开始新的停火谈判，试图解除哈马斯的武装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/israel-to-start-talks-on-phase-2-ceasefire-deal-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列将早在本周与哈马斯的停火第二阶段开始谈判，以旨在将巴勒斯坦集团在加沙的完全拆除。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/israel-to-start-talks-on-phase-2-ceasefire-deal-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 10:46:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市市长在霍克尔与民主党会面时被迫被迫被迫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/four-senior-adams-aides-resign-amid-calls-for-nyc-mayor-to-quit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州长凯西·霍克尔（Kathy Hochul）正在对埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）政府的未来提出“严重的疑问”，理由是她罢免市长的权力，因为她呼吁周二与主要领导人在曼哈顿办事处开会，讨论前进的道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/four-senior-adams-aides-resign-amid-calls-for-nyc-mayor-to-quit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 21:29:33 GMT</pubDate>
